@REM==============================================================================

@node "PreRelease" "Pre-Release Informations"

                            @{b}Pre-Release Informations
                           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

FAME is a brand new MailBox program which seems to be becomimg very popular
and FAMEous as we can tell from the very positive reactions we receive
daily.

We already have many bug-reports and suggestions and we believe we will
get lots more from the very first release on.

We work hard on fixing all reported bugs and act on suggestions as best we
can, but it's impossible to do all at the same time.

The same with the documents.
The documents are not complete at all... we still have to enhance and enlarge
the documents to relate to the FAME executables.

You have bought FAME in an early stage and because of this not everything
written here is 100% correct, but we work on it.


@{u}@{b}Known undescribed parts in FAMEFileChecker.guide@{uu}@{ub}

 - None.


@{b}@{u}Additional@{ub}@{uu}

 - FAMEFileChecker isn't 100% Complete.
   It does background file checkings, but FileId description and
   file postings to the conference will follow next.

@endnode

